title: For Sale:  Russian Tigr SVD Dragunov
location: South Carolina, South Carolina, United States
postcontent: This is the famous Russian SVD "Dragunov Sniper Rifle". This weapon was manufactured by the Izhmash arms factory in Izhevsk Russia and imported by California Armory Inc, San Bruno, California. The rifle has been given the nickname "California Tiger" by collectors and is recognized as being among the best and most collectible Dragunov style rifles available in the United States. Originally, there were to be 1000 of these rifles imported but far fewer actually made it into the country. Chambered for the 7.62x54r (just like the original), this rifle has a 20.9" barrel and is equipped with a flash hider and bayonet mount. The various major parts are serial numbered and all matching (except the flash hider) and it comes with a new condition Russian PSO-1 detachable scope that is also serial numbered to the rifle. Condition is excellent, as new, and the weapon shows only a few light handling & storage marks. I would grade the rifle at 99% overall.
